  "elements": [
    {
      "id": "306rhdcwF6ta8eB0JFR9A",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2002.8853106167055,
      "y": 328.37305496105006,
      "width": 749.5794677734375,
      "height": 925,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a1",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 593710891,
      "version": 1476,
      "versionNonce": 1228439813,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779221873346,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Problem\n- Collect and aggregagre data on ad clicks\n- Advertisers will use this to\n    - track ad performance\n    - optimise their campaigns\n- Assume ads are displayed on a website\n\n\nFunctional Requirements\n- In scope\n    - Users click on an ad and get redirected to the advertiser's website\n    - Advertisers can query click metrics over time w/ 1 minute min granularity\n\n- Out of scope\n    - Ad targeting and serving\n    - Cross device tracking\n    - Integration with offline channels\n\n\nNon-functional Requirements\n- High throughput -> 10M ads at any given time\n- Low latency analytics queries < 1s\n- Fault tolerance\n- Data integrity\n- Freshness -> real-time\n- Scalability => 10k ad clicks per second at peak\n- Idempotency of ad clicks\n    - Op is applied multiple times, effect on system is unchanged\n    - it's as if it only happened once\n\n\n-- out of scop\n- Spam detection\n- Demographic profiling\n- Conversion tracking\n- Safety\n- Correctness",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Problem\n- Collect and aggregagre data on ad clicks\n- Advertisers will use this to\n    - track ad performance\n    - optimise their campaigns\n- Assume ads are displayed on a website\n\n\nFunctional Requirements\n- In scope\n    - Users click on an ad and get redirected to the advertiser's website\n    - Advertisers can query click metrics over time w/ 1 minute min granularity\n\n- Out of scope\n    - Ad targeting and serving\n    - Cross device tracking\n    - Integration with offline channels\n\n\nNon-functional Requirements\n- High throughput -> 10M ads at any given time\n- Low latency analytics queries < 1s\n- Fault tolerance\n- Data integrity\n- Freshness -> real-time\n- Scalability => 10k ad clicks per second at peak\n- Idempotency of ad clicks\n    - Op is applied multiple times, effect on system is unchanged\n    - it's as if it only happened once\n\n\n-- out of scop\n- Spam detection\n- Demographic profiling\n- Conversion tracking\n- Safety\n- Correctness",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "2pl46QIKlrYjQHRCH17N6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2913.7102884650963,
      "y": 318.5197824933651,
      "width": 365.71978759765625,
      "height": 525,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a3",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 687703531,
      "version": 887,
      "versionNonce": 2075649829,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779221903378,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Data Flow\n - Input\n     - click data\n     - Advertiser Queries\n\n- Output\n    - Redirection\n    - Aggregated Click metrics\n\nProcess\n- Click data comes into system\n- User is redirected\n- Click data validated\n- click data logged\n- click data aggregated\n- aggregated data queried\n\n\n\nAd impression => instance of an ad\n- same ad can occur on Mon, Tuesday",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Data Flow\n - Input\n     - click data\n     - Advertiser Queries\n\n- Output\n    - Redirection\n    - Aggregated Click metrics\n\nProcess\n- Click data comes into system\n- User is redirected\n- Click data validated\n- click data logged\n- click data aggregated\n- aggregated data queried\n\n\n\nAd impression => instance of an ad\n- same ad can occur on Mon, Tuesday",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
